No. 521,

Misc.

Mills v. Colorado. Mr. Justice Douglas is of the opinion that certiorari should be granted. Samuel D. Menin for petitioner. Duke W. Dunbar, Attorney-General of Colorado, Frank E. Hickey, Deputy Attorney General, and J. F. Brauer, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Supreme Court of Colorado. Certiorari denied.
